in basis {a1, a2, ...}. MatrixIn[op, {a1, a2, ...}, {b1, b2, ...}] returns a \
matrix with elements Bra[{ai}] op Ket[{bj}]. MatrixIn[op, assoc] returns an \
association of matrices calculated from elements of assoc. MatrixIn[op, \
assoc1, assoc2] returns an association of matrices calculated using elements \
